RELEASE iNFOS

BurnAware Professional is a powerful CD, DVD and BD disc
burning solution intended for users who need maximum control
over every aspect of the burning process and use multiple
burners for mass-production of various discs and quick creation
of disc-to-disc copies. Its a solid piece of software that will help
you cope with your daily burning tasks faster and more efficiently.

iNSTALL NOTES

1. Unpack & Install.
2. Copy/Replace FFF.NFO, burnaware.bin and install.bat files into
burnaware directory
3. Execute install.bat

Note: If you are french, Burnaware will use will use the language
file "french.lng". In french version, if you are a registered user
and if you open the About panel twice, it will crash the program.
So, don't open the About panel twice or delete this french.lng file.

Special note:

On some antivirus scans, FFF releases packages can reveal
"Type_Win32" or "Trojan_Type" virus...
Don't be stupid! It is not a virus nor anything else like
that. It is just some packers/cryptors which have the
same binary signature.
